Node "2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Listen to me stranger, this community lives forever on the brink of collapse. This is the most inhospitable place imaginable: we need all the fortune we can get, and your cack-handed attempt at repairing our AutoDoc will cost lives. Now, I'll ask you again: what do you want?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Whatever, they would've died anyway. Tell me something." linkto "5"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm really sorry about that. Can I ask you something?" linkto "6a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Nothing, I'm leaving." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I am Alexander, first among equals. I take care of the day-to-day business of Sandover: organizing duties and settling disputes between Scabs and so on. I'm also in charge of trade."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Then you're the man I'm looking for." linkto "4"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Good to know. I'll be back if I have any questions." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "4"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
