          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, if you don't mind, I had a few questions for you." linkto "6a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_BAD playertext "Who I am is none of your business, and I'm here to ask you some questions." linkto "5"  notes ""
