Node "10"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "The old days? [He flashed a sardonic smile] I'm not sure if you've noticed, but not much of the old days has survived. What makes you think your GAI is an exception?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I have no choice - it's the only hope for my people" linkto "11"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_GOOD playertext "It's all still there, it's just been... rearranged." linkto "12"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What about you Scabs? You live off what has survived from the old days." linkto "13"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Good point. Let me ask something else." linkto "6b"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "11"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Oh? Well then, I wish you the best of luck. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It's not luck I need, it's information. Are you sure you don't know anything about GAI?" linkto "14"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks. Can I ask you something else?" linkto "6c"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You can keep your wishes, I'm leaving." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "12"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Rearranged? [he laughs] I only wish I could share your optimism."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well that's how you Scabs make a living, isn't it? Off the remains of the old days?" linkto "13"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So you really don't know anything about GAI?" linkto "14"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "And I only wish you were even vaguely helpful. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "13"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "True, true. But we only pass on what we find, and it takes great knowledge to reassemble it. Looking for one specific building in that rubble - now that's quite an undertaking."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You really don't know anything else about GAI?" linkto "14"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about something else." linkto "6b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well, I'm off to undertake it." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
