Node "16"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Well, the thanks and lives of many Scabs are owed to you. Is there anything I can help you with?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm looking for the GAI headquarters." linkto "7"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I had some questions." linkto "6c"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "17"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Sandover is home to the Scabs, and the sick. There is poison in these grounds, slowly killing all of us."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "The guard at the entrance said that you were all outcasts." linkto "18"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why do you live here, if it's killing you all?" linkto "19"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "And you're in charge?" linkto "21"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Peachy. I had another question." linkto "6b"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "17a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Sandover is home to the Scabs. It is not a safe place to be."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "The guard at the entrance said that you were all outcasts." linkto "18b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why do you live here, if it's killing you all?" linkto "19a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "And you're in charge?" linkto "45"  notes ""
