Node "18"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Outcasts? Maybe once, a long time ago - the first to live here were, I'm sure of that. But nowadays its just the sick - most already have it when they arrive. They come here to die."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why would they come here, of all places?" linkto "19"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "And you?" linkto "20"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "19"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Everybody dies, but nobody likes to be reminded of it. When you get sick, most towns just forget that you exist - you don't have anything left to contribute. Here it's different, we're all in the same boat. It's not an easy life, but it's better than what you get on the outside."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What about you?" linkto "20"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "But why live on poisoned ground?" linkto "22"  notes "[Science<30%]"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "But why live in an area of high radiation?" linkto "22"  notes "[Science>30%]"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sure. Let me ask you about something else." linkto "6b"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "20"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "What about me?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Are you sick as well?" linkto "24"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How did you end up here?" linkto "26"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You're in charge, right?" linkto "21"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Never mind. Something else..." linkto "6b"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "21"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I am the first among equals. I have no right to bend a person to my will, but for all intents and purposes I am in charge, yes."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Are you sick as well?" linkto "24"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How did you end up here?" linkto "26"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Perhaps you can answer some questions for me, then." linkto "6b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Good luck with that. I'm leaving." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "22"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "The wreckage here has been disturbed little since the war - precisely because of the poison. Once hope is lost, fear goes with it and the hopeless have a slim chance of comfort in their final days."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Comfort? You call this comfort?" linkto "23"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What are you talking about?" linkto "48"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I understand. I had more questions." linkto "6b"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "23"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "If it does not meet your high standards, feel free to depart."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Alexander, do you believe in moral scalability?" linkto "58"  notes "Bad karma+high int/speech"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I had some questions first." linkto "6a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll do that." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "24"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I am not the man I was when I arrived here, but for that I have age to thank. The poison has not taken me yet."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why don't you leave, while you still can?" linkto "25"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "When did you arrive here?" linkto "26"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well, here's hoping. Later." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "25"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Where would I go? What would I achieve? I have everything I need here in Sandover, not to mention a responsibility to its inhabitants."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you something else." linkto "6b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well, it's your funeral. Tell me something else." linkto "6a"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "26"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "First time I saw Sandover I was still working for the caravans. This was a long time ago, when the place still had some life left in it. The Scabs had hit a good seam of pre-war tech, well-preserved, worth a fortune in the right hands."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "MORE" linkto "27"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "27"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I stuck around for a while to try and find the source, the company wanted to send a team in for the heavy stuff. My wife, Imogen, she was going to come with the team."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You agreed to stay here? Brave decision." linkto "28"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Couldn't you just get the Scabs to tell you where it was?" linkto "29"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about your wife." linkto "33"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see. Tell me something else." linkto "6b"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "28"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Well I was young, and greedy. The company gave me meds for the poison, and I never planned on staying for long. Just until I could find the source."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Why didn't you just ask the Scabs?" linkto "29"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Did you find it?" linkto "30"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "29"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "That lot? You'd sooner drink out of a stone. Scabs are an insular people, they always have been. As far as they were concerned, I was just a nosy outsider trying to hustle in on their salvage. I paid my keep and they let me stay. Beyond that, I was on my own."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Did you ever find it?" linkto "30"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "30"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I found it alright. There was a cave beneath one of the old buildings, got sealed off when the whole place collapsed. But the Scabs had a way in, that was how all the gear turned up at the trading table."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Did you get a message to your company?" linkto "31a"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Then why did you stay?" linkto "31b"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Will you tell me where it was? It might be the place I'm looking for." linkto "46"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "This is fascinating, but I have to go." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "31a"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Yes sir I did, I sent a message to them on the next caravan passing. Only when they got here - the haulin' crew and all - Imogen wasn't with them. Turns out they'd been attacked by raiders on the journey south - she was cut down where she stood."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm sorry to hear that." linkto "32"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It's a dangerous world." linkto "34"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Could you show me where you found the building?" linkto "46"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "31b"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Well, I found the source of the salvage, got a message to the company on the next caravan passing. Only when they got here - the crew and all - Imogen wasn't with them. They told me she'd been killed by raiders not three days earlier."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm sorry to hear that." linkto "32"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It's a dangerous world." linkto "34"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Death is only nature's way of telling you you're a weakling. Tell me something else." linkto "5"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How terrible. Let me change the subject." linkto "6b"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "32"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Oh I was too, I was for the longest time. I just froze up, I couldn't do, or think, anything. I just stayed here, in the cave I paid for, crying over what I'd lost."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "And you never left?" linkto "40"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "33"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Imogen? She and me got together when I was barely twenty years old. Me, I never believed in all that 'love-at-first-sight' - still don't, but that didn't stop me at the time. [He smiles wistfully] Poor Mog..."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What happened to her?" linkto "31b"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "34"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "It is, it truely is - after lost Imogen, I couldn't stand to face it any more. I just froze up, didn't think anything, didn't do anything. Just stayed here, in the cave I paid for, crying over what I'd lost."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "And you never left?" linkto "40"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "35"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Saman is a bitter man, quick to blame everyone and everything other than himself.  He is good at his job, though, and follows orders well enough."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Is there something between you two?" linkto "-1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you about someone else." linkto "39"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I had some other questions." linkto "6b"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "36"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Look around you. Without the meagre supplies we receive we wouldn't last a month. The traders know this, and so do we."
 NPCFemaleText "My dear, take a look around. Without the meagre supplies we receive we wouldn't last a month, and the traders know that."
